"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-14-team-gb-star-completed-olympics-marathon-broken-leg-downhills-hell-21421435\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB's Rose Harvey competed the women's marathon at the 2024Olympic GamesinPariswith a broken leg and says the 'downhills were hell'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999898768890834, \"rank\": 6.737250374853881e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9999930577516766, \"rank\": 6.479851310248053e-06, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"score\": 0.9989603592887549, \"rank\": 0.0006713034019561958, \"text\": \"Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old runner completed Sunday's race in two hours, 51 minutes and three seconds - which saw her finish 78th - on the final day of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Harvey has now taken toInstagramto reveal the 'heartbreaking' news of her leg break, and how she did not let it stop her from fulfilling her Olympic dream in Paris.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999948854112, \"rank\": 5.1145890667933096e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This was far from the Olympics I dreamed of, but still an experience of a lifetime,' Great Britain's Olympic star Harvey posted, with a picture of herself on crutches.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"score\": 0.9989603592887549, \"rank\": 0.0006713034019561958, \"text\": \"Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was so excited to step on that stage, show that I had what it takes to be part of Team GB and most importantly, do everyone proud who has helped me get to this point.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999898768890834, \"rank\": 6.737250374853881e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And just a couple of weeks ago, it was looking so good.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Training had been stellar.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I developed a bit of tightness in my hip.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'My incredible team and I put in so much work to make the start line fit and healthy, and we were all optimistic that with a bit of race day adrenaline I would be able to run the race I knew I had in me.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'A couple of miles in, I quickly realised that wasn't going to happen.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next 24 miles were a painful battle.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It turns out I had stress fractured my femur.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'In any other race, I would have stopped and there were so many moments when I thought I could not take another step.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The downhills were hell.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But despite that most of my race goals having slipped away, there was still a tiny part of my Olympic dream that I could hang on to - and that was finishing the Olympic marathon.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I could not give up.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I kept telling myself to smile, soak up the energy of the incredible crowds and just put one foot in front of the other.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was heartbreaking.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But being part of the Olympics is something I will never forget and being able to share the race with so many of my amazing friends and family meant the world to me.'\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star Adam Peaty makes retirement decision after Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Russia says Paris Olympics' closing ceremony was 'obvious Satanism'  ArrowMORE:JK Rowling and Elon Musk named in Imane Khelif 'cyber harassment' lawsuit after Olympics win  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9771801031804525, \"rank\": 0.022590341342879888, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"h